A firetruck follows a wildfire on Mount Hymittos in the suburb of Peania near Athens on Monday. Greek firefighters brought under control a major forest fire fanned by strong winds, officials said. At least two houses were burned but there were no reports of injuries as police quickly evacuated the area and blocked roads. Photo: AFP Â  
